{"tid":1520862,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【廢老燒熄】：果然又再次破戒，再一而再、再而三四五六七對運動指指點點","createTime":"2019-08-31T03:31:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-31T07:39:00.000Z","uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"a2578c01eb3565291eea679e562b5e63681f5622","tid":1520862,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T03:31:37.000Z","msg":"【廢老燒熄】：果然又再次破戒，再一而再、再而三四五六七對運動指指點點<br />\n<br />\n1. 勇武抗爭已係十九世紀做嘅事，而家世界潮流係和理非<br />\n<br />\n2. 我唔認同甘地咁要比差佬任扑，但和平集會亦唔係不合作運動<br />\n<br />\n3. 用汽油彈係唔拖唔水，極愚蠢嘅事，係你就用莫洛托夫雞尾酒，加鐵釘同毒藥整死人──不過我反對暴力<br />\n<br />\n4. 由於我唔認同勇武抗爭，所以我唔會上街（但佢無解釋咁耐以黎除咗冷氣軍師，佢做咗啲乜9嘢公民抗命同不合作運動）<br />\n<br />\n5. 要將擲汽油彈同打警察嘅片upload上連登，然後要連登大台決定呢班人係咪違反抗爭底線，如果係嘅話往後連登大台就要宣佈所有做呢啲行為嘅全部都係鬼<br />\n<br />\n6. 岑子杰作為公眾人物真係好蠢，佢根本唔應該去啲普通餐廳食飯，佢應該要時刻搵人保護佢，同埋去食飯要揀啲對住門口嘅位坐，有咩依郁就要從後門走<br />\n<br />\n7. 即使間舖頭係同黑社會有聯繫，唔能別走去打爛人地舖頭<br />\n<br />\n8. 去遊行可以戴口罩，但戴豬嘴同包實哂自己就完全不能接受<br />\n<br />\n9. 其實去遊行根本唔需要蒙面，怕比人認出／比老闆炒你遊行行後啲，帶CAP帽遮下就得<br />\n<br />\n10. 831之前係咁拉人係林鄭毒計，目的係引誘抗爭者使用武力，然後搵藉口引入《緊急法》進行全面搜捕，所以勇武派如果搞勇武抗爭，就係中哂計<br />\n<br />\n11. 和理非公民抗命係「滴水穿石」，隨時要等三五十年先會成功（不如講夠三五百年丫笨）<br />\n<br />\n12. 基於我同情後生仔，所以你地搞出黎啲抗爭就算搞禍我檔生意，都唔會怪責你地<br />\n<br />\n13. 睇黎差佬好快拉到我，我都預咗坐幾個月監，到時拎兩本書入去睇（屌，無人想拉你呀，好心自量下啦）<br />\n<br />\n14. 應承各位網友，我係會同全香港人一齊走到最後（全部網友鼓掌），但係<span style=\"color: red;\">我都會將啲資產轉移哂做美金，同埋我將會去台灣移民</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/250391165056764/posts/2375003835928809?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F250391165056764%2Fposts%2F2375003835928809%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=7zzHsEpI0SCc5dEpMOtc2X%2B3Qbouwy6U%2BTFwRHAqvaY%3D&h=e0b7cf6a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/250391165056764/posts/2375003835928809?sfns=mo</a>"},{"pid":"ae08540523126abd1149239276c62ae5b8363272","tid":1520862,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T04:21:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4a242d09ad5ccbcc48d5ff542aaa18c16ff2d50","tid":1520862,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T05:39:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbbf69185cd56c25d1936fe064c2b700cd594b7f","tid":1520862,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T05:55:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31b210d475a9d00169cf2e1bb2c22008f89a0bb6","tid":1520862,"uid":224479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T05:56:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07c1c10658df4aacc4b44598dec2bd276169e822","tid":1520862,"uid":53803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T07:37:10.000Z","msg":"燒山真係幫到好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n燈下燈下燈到香港獨立"},{"pid":"149b75686063279bc87ce4c5103a96e611985826","tid":1520862,"uid":189235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T07:38:12.000Z","msg":"自燈 高招<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de5350e8845a9911658d751b7894e1261b4fde47","tid":1520862,"uid":208452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T07:39:00.000Z","msg":"請支持國難五金西環店<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1521301/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1521301/page/1</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces